This Collection Value Tracker function provides comprehensive management of a watch collection with several key features:

Collection Management:

Add watches to the collection with detailed information
Update watch details including current valuations
Remove watches from the collection


Value Tracking:

Record valuation history for each watch
Track overall collection value over time
Calculate appreciation/depreciation


Performance Analysis:

Identify best and worst performing watches
Analyze performance by brand
Calculate overall collection return on investment


Collection Insights:

Generate brand distribution statistics
Create value distribution across price ranges
Build acquisition timeline and value timeline
Calculate average holding period for watches


Reporting:

Generate comprehensive collection reports
Provide detailed summary statistics
Show performance metrics across different dimensions



The function is designed with a flexible action-based approach, allowing collectors to build and manage their collection over time while gaining valuable investment insights.
